<view class="page-shell battle-lobby">
  <view class="page-title">双人竞速</view>
  <view class="page-subtitle">两个人面对同一个隐藏词，90 秒内先猜中者获胜。</view>

  <view class="battle-visual surface">
    <view class="player-orb left">你</view>
    <view class="versus">VS</view>
    <view class="player-orb right">友</view>
    <view class="battle-line"></view>
  </view>

  <button class="primary-button create-button" loading="{{creating}}" disabled="{{creating || checking}}" bindtap="createRoom">创建双人房间</button>

  <view class="join-divider"><text></text><view>加入好友房间</view><text></text></view>

  <view class="join-panel surface">
    <input class="room-input" value="{{joinCode}}" maxlength="6" placeholder="六位房间码" bindinput="onCodeInput" confirm-type="done" bindconfirm="joinRoom" />
    <button class="secondary-button" loading="{{joining}}" disabled="{{joining || joinCode.length !== 6}}" bindtap="joinRoom">加入比赛</button>
  </view>

  <view class="battle-rules">
    <view><text>1</text><view>两人到齐后，由房主开始比赛</view></view>
    <view><text>2</text><view>只同步次数和最高相似度，不泄露猜词</view></view>
    <view><text>3</text><view>结束后双方确认，即可原房间再战</view></view>
  </view>
</view>
